      <title>英国外长斯塔默将在阿联酋和沙特之行期间推动海湾贸易协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/uk-s-starmer-to-push-for-gulf-trade-deal-during-uae-saudi-trip</link>
