      <title>特朗普幽灵引发最后一轮利率调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫引发全球贸易动荡的可能性上升之前，四大洲的央行将在未来一周对借贷成本做出最后一系列调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《信贷周刊》：创纪录的杠杆贷款交易掩盖了新兴脆弱性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/record-leveraged-loan-deals-mask-emerging-frailty-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，债券市场一直处于风险模式，美联储降息和唐纳德·特朗普当选美国总统的刺激因素不断升温。自 8 月初以来，垃圾债券的风险溢价已下跌逾 1 个百分点，公司上周推出了约 1050 亿美元的杠杆贷款，创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/record-leveraged-loan-deals-mask-emerging-frailty-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>X 的 Yaccarino 赞扬儿童安全法案并敦促众议院支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/x-s-yaccarino-praises-child-safety-bill-and-urges-house-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆马斯克的X社交媒体服务和美国主要参议员就一项两党网络安全法案的措辞达成一致，以保护儿童免受欺凌和剥削，首席执行官琳达亚卡里诺说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/x-s-yaccarino-praises-child-safety-bill-and-urges-house-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 18:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚阿萨德遭围困并向美国示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/syria-s-besieged-assad-makes-overtures-to-us-in-bid-to-survive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，随着叙利亚反对派武装越来越接近首都，总统巴沙尔·阿萨德正在做出最后的努力以继续掌权，包括向美国和当选总统唐纳德·特朗普发出间接的外交提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/syria-s-besieged-assad-makes-overtures-to-us-in-bid-to-survive</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 18:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙欢迎特朗普访问巴黎爱丽舍宫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-07/macron-welcomes-trump-to-elysee-palace-in-paris-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙欢迎美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普来到爱丽舍宫，庆祝巴黎圣母院重新开放。两国领导人谈到了两国之间的团结和友谊，特朗普表示，两人将讨论一个“有点疯狂”的世界。
（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-07/macron-welcomes-trump-to-elysee-palace-in-paris-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 17:23:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克电力产量因针对基础设施的抗议活动而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/mozambique-power-output-cut-by-protests-targeting-infrastructure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于针对 10 月 9 日有争议的选举的持续抗议活动，两座主要发电厂的发电量中断，莫桑比克南部地区（包括首都马普托）的电力供应减少了约三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/mozambique-power-output-cut-by-protests-targeting-infrastructure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 16:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普抵达爱丽舍宫与马克龙会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-07/trump-arrives-at-elysee-palace-for-meeting-with-macron-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普自 11 月赢得美国总统大选以来首次出访海外。他抵达巴黎爱丽舍宫，与法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙会面，出席巴黎圣母院重新开放仪式。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-07/trump-arrives-at-elysee-palace-for-meeting-with-macron-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
